<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="4" n="73">방 쳠 군셔</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="4" n="74">부 본졈으로 왕림시면</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="4" n="75">본졈 솜틀에 도셔가</sent>
